良入讀香港大學歷史系。</blockquote> <br />\n<br />\n當年無乜話父幹，佢屋企至少唔係住籠屋木屋區低薪收入嗰啲工廠難民，但留意呢度<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>祖父曾居於美國，父親是秘魯華僑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個重要，屋企人喺言語間，講番舊事嗰陣俾到咩視野個細路，對佢成長嘅心態同取向有好大影響"},{"pid":"ddce705ede57d39c102370f70dbf6a00aa5f5ef9","tid":2267182,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"47fd3a69bb7bc9b7197ea2eeec4261eb49dda22c","tid":2267182,"uid":1275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:50:27.000Z","msg":"你未聽過佢科網股爆破一鋪輸身家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連佢家姐間上市公司都要賤賣喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:53:29.000Z","msg":"咁係佢生意失敗者 關家境咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點解而家又好似唔等錢用咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63308bf3718e03afe517519672f37c6772b535c","tid":2267182,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f25d9a2fba06a88dfc40b9d3b14c4b990dfcbe63","tid":2267182,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:54:35.000Z","msg":"接手屋企生意咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞飲食 超市電影為咩"},{"pid":"5db1e9d4951aba2f787118b4e552ffc233ad2f46","tid":2267182,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd5f28b79517dea22aa8a4c8d60e78483e0f5011","tid":2267182,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f2cbbc03d6f73248ef46cbe3992086ded757baf5","tid":2267182,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4e57bbdf8a632163009a90e7ee906a948f2c216e","tid":2267182,"uid":10637,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T01:43:16.000Z","msg":"佢本身已經係醒目同叻<br />\n果個年代入到hku<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/